author: kim scerine
title: kim scerine
text: Unita was my sales rep. I was shopping for a formal and was the only adult customer surrounded by high school girls shopping for prom. :) Unita did an outstanding job in bringing me multiple options. I bought one formal and will be back next month for another one. I had sooo much fun with your staff.
